# Tailwind CSS v4 & Design System

## Config

No `tailwind.config.ts` — all tokens are defined via `@theme inline` in `src/app/globals.css`.

## Breakpoints

| Token | Width | Use for |
|-------|-------|---------|
| `sm:` | 600px | Small tablets |
| `md:` | 920px | Tablets / small laptops |
| `lg:` | 1224px | Desktops |
| `xl:` | 1440px | Wide screens |

## Brand Colours

| Token | Hex | Use |
|-------|-----|-----|
| `primary-500` | `#5025d1` | Main purple |
| `primary-600` | `#2f1c6a` | Dark purple |
| `pink-500` | `#fc5185` | CTA buttons, accents |
| `pink-600` | `#d63163` | Hover state |
| `plum-900` | `#3d1f3a` | Hero dark background |
| `plum-800` | `#4a2249` | Hero gradient mid |
| `orange-500` | `#fea419` | Star ratings, highlights |
| `teal-500` | `#00b090` | Success states |

Never use raw hex values in components — use the token names above.

## Fonts

- **`font-heading`**: Mynerve (cursive) — headings, section titles
- **`font-body`**: Montserrat (sans-serif) — body text (default)

## Utility Classes (globals.css)

- `.glass-card` / `.glass-card-strong` — frosted glass effect
- `.animated-gradient` / `.animated-gradient-slow` — background animation
- `.gradient-orb` — decorative blurred orb
- `.section-divider` — subtle gradient line
- `.scrollbar-hide` — hide scrollbar for carousels
- `.feature-card-1` through `.feature-card-4` — feature grid variants

## Shadows

Use `shadow-card` for card elements, `shadow-card-hover` for hover states.
Avoid Tailwind defaults (`shadow-sm/md/lg`) — use the project tokens instead.
